      "narrator_chain": {
        "parts": [
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "فَاتَّقِ اللهَ، وَارْدُدْ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " إِلَى "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "هَؤُلَاءِ الْقَوْمِ أمَوَالَهُمْ، فإِنَّكَ إِنْ لَمْ تَفْعَلْ ثُمَّ أَمْكَنَنِي اللهُ مِنْكَ لَأُعْذِرَنَّ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " إِلَى "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "اللهِ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " فِي"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:2:41:6",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/2/41/210",
      "text": [
        "كَ، وَلَأَضْرِبَنَّكَ بِسَيْفِي الَّذِي مَا ضَرَبْتُ بِهِ أَحَداً إِلَّا دَخَلَ النَّارَ!"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "Fear Allāh and return to these people their properties. If you do not do so and Allāh grants me power over you I shall excuse myself before Allāh about you and strike you with my sword with which I did not strike anyone but that he went to Hell."
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.sayed-ali-raza"
    ]
  },
